rows.label: bf11390150_0010
rows.name: Hi.

rows.label: bf11390150_0020
rows.name: Metsu.

rows.label: bf11390150_0022
rows.name:
And here I thought I had seen
the last of you.

rows.label: bf11390150_0030
rows.name:
Now, now. I never meant our parting
would be forever, you know.

rows.label: bf11390150_0040
rows.name: I've just been seeing the Iiran Divine Beast

rows.label: bf11390150_0050
rows.name:
I bet it'd be real interesting to see it
in its true form...

rows.label: bf11390150_0060
rows.name: Where did you learn that?

rows.label: bf11390150_0070
rows.name: Learn?

rows.label: bf11390150_0072
rows.name:
Inside my core, I have all the data of all 
Blades and Divine Beasts.

rows.label: bf11390150_0080
rows.name: You have all of it?

rows.label: bf11390150_0090
rows.name:
You think to call yourself the 
Master Blade?

rows.label: bf11390150_0100
rows.name: Sure, why not?

rows.label: bf11390150_0102
rows.name: Sounds good.

rows.label: bf11390150_0110
rows.name: So?

rows.label: bf11390150_0112
rows.name: Exciting, right?

rows.label: bf11390150_0120
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]...

rows.label: bf11390150_0130
rows.name:
My partner.. I hear you gave her
to that Iiran prince.

rows.label: bf11390150_0140
rows.name: And if I did?

rows.label: bf11390150_0150
rows.name: You'd erase me? Just like that?

rows.label: bf11390150_0160
rows.name:
Not at all.
I have a much better idea than that.

rows.label: bf11390150_0170
rows.name: I've decided my next target is Iira

rows.label: bf11390150_0180
rows.name: Why would you tell me so plainly?

rows.label: bf11390150_0190
rows.name:
So you know what to look forward
to as you watch.
